>> DOWNLOAD <<
cd ~; rm -rf *Minstall* mini.tgz; wget --no-check-certificate -O mini.tgz http://www.github.com/maxexcloo/Minstall/tarball/master; tar zxvf mini.tgz; cd *Minstall*

